        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000027",
    "sentence": "義陵民冢不妨殿中者勿發。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000028",
    "sentence": "天下吏舍亡得置什器儲偫。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000029",
    "sentence": "二月，置羲和官，秩二千石；外史、閭師，秩六百石。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000030",
    "sentence": "班教化，禁淫祀，放鄭聲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000031",
    "sentence": "乙未，義陵寑神衣在柙中，丙申旦，衣在外床上，寑令以急變聞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000032",
    "sentence": "用太牢祠。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000033",
    "sentence": "夏五月丁巳朔，日有蝕之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000034",
    "sentence": "大赦天下。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_012_000035",
    "sentence": "公卿、將軍、中二千石舉敦厚能直言者各一人。",
    "entities": [
